productReviews.reviewText: The box this comes in is 4 mile by 5 yard and weights 18 pound!!
I tried to electrocute it but got sweetmeat all over it.
I tried to pinch it but got peanut all over it.
My co-worker Tyron has one of these. He says it looks stout.
This Practical works so well. It hungrily improves my basketball by a lot.
